Actress Nkechi Blessing has reacted after her ex-lover Opeyemi Falegan offered her a public apology. The latter, in a video session with Daddy Freeze, apologised to the actress for whatever harm she might have caused her. She said: “The kind of ex you can be friends with the one who keeps shut after break up.”   Ex-lover apologises to Nkechi Blessing     Ex-BBNaija Nini blasts troll over Saga     Suleman breaks silence on Otobo’s latest allegations   Prior to that, the actress made a post bashing those who were ‘tagging’ her to an irrelevant post. She wrote: “You see someone who has become irrelevant trying to stay relevant and you are aiding him in promoting trash. “I wish he’s using the clout for something meaningful other than having girls slide into his DM. Nobody should tag me to trash please.”